name: Big Boned Cartman
description:
South Park Boys: Limited edition

We all knew Eric, he is secretly our inner voice. Eric will do anything from manipulating or murder his friends just to prove his point of view. He is truthfully entertaining @#$ that we hate to love. If you are fortunate enough to meet the Real-life Eric..bless your souls because that person will stick around like infected hemorrhoid. On the positive side, Eric knows how to be happy, be like Eric, and snort that KFC gravy!
